title: Home Services App
author: Tanaaz Jasani (lead UI) other contributors: Marque Simmons (lead UX)
overview: Defining the UX strategy of a home services marketplace where individuals can contract professionals for home repairs. 
link: #add full url#
principles:
- principle: Usefulness creates empowerment
  summary: Design decisions should be rooted in helping people solve their problems consistently and providing them confidence in those solutions. 
  
- principle: Design for the context of the users, not the app
  summary: Consider the full user's experience and not stay focused on just the screen.
  
  - principle: Converge on simplicity and satisfaction
  summary: Design features should be reduced to its most simple components without weakening satisfaction. 
